OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely cloudy overnight, perhaps with
OL,7,Fa few breaks in the cloud here and
OL,8,Fthere. Further outbreaks of patchy
OL,9,Fdrizzle likely especially over the
OL,10,Fhills of Cumbria.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many on
OL,13,FTuesday with further patchy drizzle.
OL,14,FHowever the cloud will lift and break
OL,15,Fmore readily during the afternoon with
OL,16,Fa strengthening southwesterly wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
